short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Display DALL-E 2 images alongside Google Images Search results

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The DALL-E 2 Google Extension brings the power of AI-generated images to your Google Images search experience. With this extension, you can see the results of your search query not only from Google Images, but also from DALL-E 2, the state-of-the-art AI model developed by OpenAI. The DALL-E 2 generated images are embedded into your Google Images search page, so you can see everything in one place.

Source code: https://github.com/alonstern/DALLE2-google-extension
